work.title: Sov ind, mit søde Nusseben!
Sleep tight, my ducky little dear

history.p: According to his diary, Nielsen composed the song on 18 December 1914.

incipText.p: Sleep tight, my ducky little dear!

annot.p: Letter of 11 Nov. 1914 from Carl Nielsen to Margrete Rosenberg.

annot.p: Printed in: Poul Martin Møller, Udvalgte Skrifter, ed. Vilhelm Andersen.
